{"tid":1833592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎蔓延    北韓急關邊界禁中国遊客","createTime":"2020-01-22T03:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:54:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"906937a9b2e051009a806ade1c629509871e443b","tid":1833592,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2019/12/30/027ededa1de9ca6186ac966b8cfd0662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2019%2F12%2F30%2F027ededa1de9ca6186ac966b8cfd0662.jpg&h=e27809b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n (AFP)<br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎有蔓延趨勢，就連鄰近的北韓也憂心忡忡，在中國的一家專營北韓旅遊的旅行社對外公告表示，北韓政府為防範新型冠狀病毒，決定無限期禁止中國遊客入境，包括春節期間大規模赴北韓旅遊的團客均全部拒絕入境。<br />\n<br />\n外媒報導指稱，總部位於中國的「Young Pioneer Tours」冒險旅遊公司在其網站發布聲明，指北韓政府為防範新型冠狀病毒，自周三(22日)起暫時對外國遊客關閉邊境。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》也報導，北韓長期受到國際社會制裁，治療和預防疾病的水準較低，因此嚴控外國遊客入境是最有效的預防方式。報導指出，2003年中國爆發SARS(嚴重急性呼吸道症候群)疫情，北韓便曾經暫停平壤至北京航線，同時關閉新義州海關，正因為這些防控措施，使得北韓當時並未受到SARS影響。<br />\n<br />\n此外，報導也引述北韓保健省國家衛生檢閱院處長姜哲晉（音）受訪談話表示，北韓正與世界衛生組織保持密切合作，加強預防新型病毒宣傳工作，在全國範圍內積極開展防控工作。北韓有關部門還提醒居民出行時戴口罩，回家勤洗手，注意個人衛生和通風消毒。<br />\n<br />\n不過因農曆春節是中國旅客大量前往北韓旅遊的高峰，且這些專營北韓團客旅遊的旅行社已經出售不少春節期間團客商品，因此北韓突然關閉邊境，勢必遭受巨大損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2048999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2048999&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=d2f864b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2048999</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gannett-cdn.com/presto/2019/10/02/USAT/b5931760-f324-4d58-b9ff-41c3dba83216-AP_Trump.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gannett-cdn.com%2Fpresto%2F2019%2F10%2F02%2FUSAT%2Fb5931760-f324-4d58-b9ff-41c3dba83216-AP_Trump.JPG&h=a2201a88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca09b74ab8e5238924cb2ac68e791c933ce937d5","tid":1833592,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"港共衰過北韓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5fd152047567ed96d67e8386698c5595fc7180","tid":1833592,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://kbimages1-a.akamaihd.net/42dd4512-497b-4bdc-beb9-5ed2727d1360/353/569/90/False/s6C8IG3Wijufbpb6MK0D4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbimages1-a.akamaihd.net%2F42dd4512-497b-4bdc-beb9-5ed2727d1360%2F353%2F569%2F90%2FFalse%2Fs6C8IG3Wijufbpb6MK0D4A.jpg&h=2eb406fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52d2077cd015c72a3fa119b8c631dd70efd84231","tid":1833592,"uid":170249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"北韓咁封閉都識玩落閘<br />\n<br />\n相反 港共高官仲係當小事<br />\n<br />\n03年sars都吸唔夠經驗？"},{"pid":"0bed91cacdc14f89400c4982ca4e0d560941bff4","tid":1833592,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d2077cd015c72a3fa119b8c631dd70efd84231","tid":1833592,"uid":170249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:35:45.000Z","msg":"北韓咁封閉都識玩落閘<br />\n<br />\n相反 港共高官仲係當小事<br />\n<br />\n03年sars都吸唔夠經驗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"都唔洗問責落台 驚閪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時咪話政府深切關懷肺炎"},{"pid":"b0dcdc19430db536bc5c6d28afc0ef3d05ae056b","tid":1833592,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"金仔 射鳩死d支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e76d3449b6119f657b62dcc193212c4c5edfff","tid":1833592,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"人地都知出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2c0c3ab0aa1dd44a15a43cf8f9b9ef15700fd4","tid":1833